---
---
<section id="process" style="padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-md); background-color: var(--color-secondary);">
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
      <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">How It Works.</h2>
      <p style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 50ch;">We have experience working with a variety of small and mid-sized businesses, helping them grow and improve through our consulting services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="asymmetric-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-xl);">
      
      <div class="animate-fade-in delay-100" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: var(--space-md);">
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-5xl); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); line-height: 0.8; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">1</div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); color: var(--color-accent);">Free Consultation</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">Talk with a professional systems engineer (typically $500+/hr) to thoroughly discuss your project requirements and objectives.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fade-in delay-300" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: var(--space-md);">
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-5xl); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); line-height: 0.8; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">2</div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); color: var(--color-accent);">Strategy & Proposal</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">Following your consultation, we will deliver a comprehensive scope, outlining itemized steps, a detailed timeline, and budget estimates.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fade-in delay-500" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: var(--space-md);">
        <div style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: var(--text-5xl); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); line-height: 0.8; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">3</div>
        <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); color: var(--color-accent);">Implementation</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base);">Upon approval, our rapid implementation process ensures that your business starts seeing results immediately with minimal effort.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
